OL,5, A senior nurse said she was targeted by
OL,6, NHS managers after she raised concerns 
OL,7, about a colleague that she alleged had 
OL,8, implications for patient safety.       
OL,10,FRebecca Wight said she and colleagues  
OL,11,Frepeatedly asked bosses to address     
OL,12,Falleged failings by a nurse at The     
OL,13,FChristie cancer hospital in Manchester.
OL,15,F"I didn't realise (speaking out) would 
OL,16,Fcause such distress and such detriment 
OL,17,Fto my life," she told BBC Newsnight.   
OL,19,FThe Christie said it was "grateful" Ms 
OL,20,FWight had raised concerns three times. 
